Package org.waarp.openr66.commander

Classes implementing Commander, reader of database updates from clients

See:
          Description


Interface Summary
CommanderInterface  
 

Class Summary
ClientRunner Client Runner from a TaskRunner
Commander Commander is responsible to read from database updated data from time to time in order to achieve new runner or new configuration updates.
CommanderNoDb Commander is responsible to read list of updated data from time to time in order to achieve new runner or new configuration updates.
InternalRunner This class launch and control the Commander and enable TaskRunner job submissions
ThreadPoolRunnerExecutor Thread Pool Executor for ClientRunner
